_:Na4c42e7f28f3446aa7d6eb22f850e0cd <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Lucy Livings started her role as Regional Director for South-West in January 2024.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to this Lucy was Deputy Director within the south-west region from 2019. Lucy is an experienced civil servant with a broad range of experience including:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>posts within the Department for International Development in Afghanistan, Zimbabwe, and in the conflict and nutrition policy teams</li>\n  <li>a 3-year secondment to the USA as Senior Advisor to the UK Executive Director of the World Bank</li>\n  <li>several years in Private Office working for three different Permanent Secretaries</li>\n</ul>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
