<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/lucy-livings> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Lucy Livings started her role as Regional Director for South-West in January 2024. Prior to this Lucy was Deputy Director within the south-west region from 2019. Lucy is an experienced civil servant with a broad range of experience including: posts within the Department for International Development in Afghanistan, Zimbabwe, and in the conflict and nutrition policy teams a 3-year secondment to the USA as Senior Advisor to the UK Executive Director of the World Bank several years in Private Office working for three different Permanent Secretaries"@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
